      "lineNbr": 32,
      "author": {
        "id": 1147264
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-01-27T20:31:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Technically speaking, this metric can contain the travel time of contents between the client and ResultDB server as well due to the its streaming implementation. It\u0027s also true for /chrome/infra/http/server_response_latency for \u0027/invocations/*rest\u0027.\n\nI\u0027m afraid that this description may sound that this latency reports the upload/download performance between RBE-CAS(stroage) and ResultDB. Could we rephrase this to be more clear?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 32,
        "startChar": 43,
        "endLine": 32,
        "endChar": 58
      },
